##### **5.3.2 How does pivoting work?**

```{r}
df <- tribble(
  ~id,  ~bp1, ~bp2,
   "A",  100,  120,
   "B",  140,  115,
   "C",  120,  125
)
```

```{r}
df |> 
  pivot_longer(
    cols = bp1:bp2,
    names_to = "measurement",
    values_to = "value"
  )
#> # A tibble: 6 × 3
#>   id    measurement value
#>   <chr> <chr>       <dbl>
#> 1 A     bp1           100
#> 2 A     bp2           120
#> 3 B     bp1           140
#> 4 B     bp2           115
#> 5 C     bp1           120
#> 6 C     bp2           125
```

